3.0 Which journeys are covered by the insurance?
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
3.1 The insurance covers business travel, holiday travel and combined
business and holiday travel all over the world, including in Denmark.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
3.2 The coverage only covers journeys lasting a maximum of 60 days. As
regards travel in the country of residence, the insured must have planned
at least one overnight stay outside the local authority where his/her
permanent residence is located.
.br
Coverage comes into effect for the individual journey when the insured
leaves his/her home address to commence the journey, and ends when he/she
returns to his/her home address.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
